summary: I’m gonna have a guitar somewhere. There’s gotta be one somewhere around here. Okay, I was thinking maybe we could have a moment...
text: I’m gonna have a guitar somewhere. There’s gotta be one somewhere around here. Okay, I was thinking maybe we could have a moment of just, like, you and me time? Just me, you, a guitar? You guys are absolutely incredible. So I haven’t gotten to play for a UK crowd in a while, and I missed you so much. I missed you so much; I missed just everything about the energy that you bring. We actually just started the Reputation Stadium Tour, and I’m so excited that I get to spend almost the entire month of June with you in the UK. We’re gonna be playing two shows in Manchester, two shows in Dublin, and two shows at Wembley in London. Sing this one if you know it.
source: Taylor talking to the crowd before performing Delicate at The Biggest Weekend in Swansea, Wales (May 27th, 2018)
